article_title: Community and Adventist teaming to create Medi-Cal health plan
article_text:
Medi-Cal health plan would be run by two largest hospital systems in central San Joaquin Valley

Plan builds off agreement Adventist Health has now with Health Net in Kings County

Will Valley Children’s specialists be providers in new plan? Maybe not.
